_sText: This is a map that i made that is half b-town and half construct from garrysmod10.. I made the whole map but of course i got the construct part from garry >.> obviously. as far as the construct part goes, i dont care if its too small  or if its not exact, because my main concern was the game play for zm, and obviously if I just remade construct w/o the other half the game play would be impossible... zombies would pwn. but of course I would still like to here some tips on how to make it better and bug fixes ect...
